text: Conque may refer to: *Conch (instrument), a wind instrument made from a conch shell ==People with the surname== *Abraham ben Levi Conque (1648 – after 1689), rabbi and kabbalist in Hebron *Clint Conque (born 1961), American college football coach ==See also== *Conch, a medium- to large-sized sea snail or shell *Conk (disambiguation) *Conquer (disambiguation) *Conques, a former commune in the Aveyron department of France
title: Conque
